FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

2025-06-27 22:45:49.905 +04:00 [INF] Route matched with {action = "GetAll", controller = "Tour"}. Executing controller action with signature System.Threading.Tasks.Task`1[Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.IActionResult] GetAll() on controller FinalProject.Controllers.Admin.TourController (FinalProject).
2025-06-27 22:45:49.917 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

2025-06-27 22:48:24.168 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (19ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

2025-06-27 23:14:07.745 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (16ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]

    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]

) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]

LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Capacity], [t].[CountryCount], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Desc], [t].[Duration], [t].[EndDate], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[OldPrice], [t].[Price], [t].[StartDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CityId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[TourId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CountryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t2].[Id], [t2].[ActivityId], [t2].[CreatedDate], [t2].[TourId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name], [t4].[Id], [t4].[AmenityId], [t4].[CreatedDate], [t4].[TourId], [t4].[Id0], [t4].[CreatedDate0], [t4].[Name], [e].[Id], [e].[CreatedDate], [e].[Name], [e].[TourId], [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Day], [p].[Description], [p].[Title], [p].[TourId]
FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]

FROM [Tours] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CityId], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[TourId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CountryId], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name]
    FROM [TourCities] AS [t1]
    INNER JOIN [Cities] AS [c] ON [t1].[CityId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t3].[Id], [t3].[ActivityId], [t3].[CreatedDate], [t3].[TourId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a].[Name]
    FROM [TourActivities] AS [t3]
    INNER JOIN [Activities] AS [a] ON [t3].[ActivityId] = [a].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t5].[Id], [t5].[AmenityId], [t5].[CreatedDate], [t5].[TourId], [a0].[Id] AS [Id0], [a0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [a0].[Name]
    FROM [TourAmenities] AS [t5]
    INNER JOIN [Amenities] AS [a0] ON [t5].[AmenityId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Experiences] AS [e] ON [t].[Id] = [e].[TourId]
LEFT JOIN [Plans] AS [p] ON [t].[Id] = [p].[TourId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [e].[Id]
